Oral versus intravenous antibiotics for bone and joint infections: the OVIVA 
non-inferiority RCT.

Scarborough M(1), Li HK(1)(2), Rombach I(3), Zambellas R(3), Walker AS(4)(5), 
McNally M(1), Atkins B(1), Kümin M(5), Lipsky BA(6), Hughes H(7), Bose D(8), 
